support_scheme_heading: Your event deserves a boost
---
support_scheme_body:

Every year, together with different supporting partners, the [Open Knowledge Foundation](https://okfn.org/en/) (OKFN) offers small financial contributions in the form of mini-grants to help promote in-person events around the world. Stay tuned to our social media channels and our newsletter to find out when the next call opens (usually in January).

In 2025, a total of 26 grants were offered in two calls (one general and the other focused on open mapping) thanks to the kind support of [Humanitarian OpenStreetMap Team](https://www.hotosm.org/) (HOT), [Jokkolabs Banjul](https://okfn.org/en/gambia/), [Open Knowledge Germany](https://okfn.de/), [Datopian](https://www.datopian.com/), and [Link Digital](https://linkdigital.com.au/).

